  "detailed_description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/1464100b79caeb719fda06e608d5799c.poster.avif?t=1728385790\" width=640 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/1464100b79caeb719fda06e608d5799c.webm?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/1464100b79caeb719fda06e608d5799c.mp4?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Survive an apocalyptic nightmare alone or with friends where you must Gather, Build, Quest, Craft, Raid and Defend what you have from the islands most terrifying mutants, monsters and horrors... the worst of them all, other players.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In-depth base building and tiered skill-based crafting system<br></li><li> RPG-Like Quest System<br></li><li> Dungeons ranging from narrow to open spaces<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/036cbdfa548a262f1d1881c92708fbf0.poster.avif?t=1728385790\" width=640 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/036cbdfa548a262f1d1881c92708fbf0.webm?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/036cbdfa548a262f1d1881c92708fbf0.mp4?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> RPG-inspired Player Progression with Talents, Abilities and Skills<br></li><li> Day/Night Cycles<br></li><li> Procedural building, road, and river systems<br></li><li> Fight players, mutants, cannibals and animals to survive<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/abf8f951f10e39d938e296e1bf569554.poster.avif?t=1728385790\" width=640 height=140 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/abf8f951f10e39d938e296e1bf569554.webm?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/abf8f951f10e39d938e296e1bf569554.mp4?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> In depth crafting, cooking, and research system<br></li><li> Open world featuring 64 square kilometer map</li></ul><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/7883d1b584f9aefc58aed2d7e4fa7e81.poster.avif?t=1728385790\" width=736 height=60 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/7883d1b584f9aefc58aed2d7e4fa7e81.webm?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/7883d1b584f9aefc58aed2d7e4fa7e81.mp4?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Explore an Open World</strong></h2>A dynamic weather system creates unpredictable hazards while the day/night system breathes life into a map based on real-world topographical data from Maui. The procedural building, road, and river system means unique worlds and environments to explore. <br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/8df14801001ce1368779278ef24d3777.poster.avif?t=1728385790\" width=640 height=208 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/8df14801001ce1368779278ef24d3777.webm?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/8df14801001ce1368779278ef24d3777.mp4?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Careful, mutants, monsters, and players lurk around every corner... Oh, and don't forget to burn the bodies, you'll want to remember that.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" ><strong>Craft and Build</strong></h2><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/c93d4a47310d39bc3757de64c11d7efd.poster.avif?t=1728385790\" width=640 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/c93d4a47310d39bc3757de64c11d7efd.webm?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/c93d4a47310d39bc3757de64c11d7efd.mp4?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Harvest resources to craft what's required to survive... Shelter, food, equipment, and of course, weapons.<br><br>AI Drones patrol the map and stream gameplay live to Twitch.tv 24/7, focusing on all things PvPvE and filming the action in standard, night-vision, spotlight, and thermal modes. Tune into the drone stream for a unique view of the game in real-time.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/5f5c8d52336c59777f9ee97d05fd62a3.poster.avif?t=1728385790\" width=640 height=132 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/5f5c8d52336c59777f9ee97d05fd62a3.webm?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/5f5c8d52336c59777f9ee97d05fd62a3.mp4?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
  "about_the_game": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/1464100b79caeb719fda06e608d5799c.poster.avif?t=1728385790\" width=640 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/1464100b79caeb719fda06e608d5799c.webm?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/1464100b79caeb719fda06e608d5799c.mp4?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Survive an apocalyptic nightmare alone or with friends where you must Gather, Build, Quest, Craft, Raid and Defend what you have from the islands most terrifying mutants, monsters and horrors... the worst of them all, other players.<h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >Features</h2><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li>In-depth base building and tiered skill-based crafting system<br></li><li> RPG-Like Quest System<br></li><li> Dungeons ranging from narrow to open spaces<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/036cbdfa548a262f1d1881c92708fbf0.poster.avif?t=1728385790\" width=640 height=144 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/036cbdfa548a262f1d1881c92708fbf0.webm?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1128500/extras/036cbdfa548a262f1d1881c92708fbf0.mp4?t=1728385790\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br></li><li> RPG-inspired Player Progression with Talents, Abilities and Skills<br></li><li> Day/Night Cycles<br></li><li> Procedural building, road, and river systems<br></li><li> Fight players, mutants, cannibals and animals to survive<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><vid